import React, {Component} from 'react'
import {
          Form, 
          FormGroup,
          Input,
          Label
        } from 'reactstrap'

class RegisterForm extends Component {
    state = {
        email: "",
        firstname: "",
        lastname: "",
        fullName: "",
        password : "",
        passwordConfirm : "",
        phoneNumber : "",
    }
    render(){
        return(
            <React.Fragment>
                <Form>
                    <FormGroup>
                        <Label>First Name:</Label>
                        <Input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Enter your first name"/>
                        <Label>Last Name:</Label>
                        <Input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Enter your last name"/>  
                    </FormGroup>
                    <FormGroup>
                        <Label>Email:</Label>
                        <Input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Enter email"/>  
                        <Label>Password:</Label>
                        <Input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Enter password"/>  
                        <Label>Confirm Password</Label>
                        <Input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Please confirm your password"/>  
                    </FormGroup>
                </Form>
            </React.Fragment>
        )
    }
}
const inputStyle = {
    padding: "10px",
    margin: "10px",
    width : "100%"
}
export default RegisterForm
